En la terminal para calcular la suma de comprobacion 

                    MD5

-----------------------------------------
Input
$ sudo su
# md5sum Hash.txt
-----------------------------------------
Output
# 82e8ac8d4ae929c79e1ce4cf1f0691f4  Hash
-----------------------------------------




*********************************************************************
En la terminal para calcular la suma de comprobacion 
                    
                    sha1

*****************************************
Input
$ sudo su
# sha1sum Hash.txt
*****************************************
Output
# 7f09aba4d0bd0541bbf424803c0550f9df2940b7  Hash
********************************************************************


--------------------------------------------------------------------
En la terminal para calcular la suma de comprobacion 
                
                sha256

-----------------------------------------
Input
$ sudo su
# sha256sum Hash.txt
-----------------------------------------
Output
# 96df8c57560d84b5d0d09c7cb1ae3a5db2501524c25edf1f3dd253a59811d610  Hash
-------------------------------------------------------------------



*******************************************************************
En la terminal para calcular la suma de comprobacion 
                
                sha512

*****************************************
Input
$ sudo su
# sha512sum Hash.txt
*****************************************
Output
# 1018826ae4aa68c92793fd0d264cbc0b8632bb60d9a72bf7f2a1a22ac7bfa391d01ae42054a6aa575dae717a755f048c9815976576632926e3d2344fb5b24177  Hash
